1:1 COMMENT "# guardnarrow.z - Post-guard flow typing"
1:41 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# A diverging branch narrows for the rest of the scope: after"
3:62 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# `if o.none then return` the condition must have been false, so `o`"
4:69 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# collapses to its remaining payload arm -- the bare name IS the payload."
5:74 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# The same applies after a match arm that exits the scope, and to the"
6:70 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# negated forms. Reassignment ends the narrowing at that point."
7:64 EOL "\n"
